cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on improving the quality of Neural Machine Translation (NMT) using sequence-to-sequence learning neural networks with attention mechanism. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a hierarchical deep neural network architecture to improve the quality of long sentences translation. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper uses deep learning techniques to improve the performance of NMT. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper proposes a neural network architecture for NMT. 
5. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is less likely but still possible as the paper uses deep learning techniques for natural language processing, which is related to computer vision and pattern recognition.
